Our previous formulas describe completely the coherent state that
is produced by this process. Just to clarify the situation a bit more
let us point out that the closed string state that is produced by
a D-instanton sitting at position  in Euclidean space is given by

  C = P_phys  e^ -d E  B 
where  is the boundary state for a D-instanton at the origin.
